{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_04_04",
  "title": "サニーピース 04 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんとはすぐに仲良くなったわ。レッスンを\n一緒に受けたり、二人で海辺を歩いて帰ったりしたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I became close with Mana-chan right away. We took lessons\ntogether and walked home together along the beach",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.2793870926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子のデビューライブでは、麻奈が楽屋で\n自分のことのように喜んでいたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At Haruko's debut live‚ Mana was so happy\nin the dressing room‚ it felt like it was her own",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4927201588,
      "endTime": 15.7373913128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈がデビューした時は、遙子さんが楽屋に来て\n二人で泣きそうになりながらハグしていましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Mana debuted‚ Haruko-san came to the dressing room‚\nhugged each other‚ and almost cried",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9440577506,
      "endTime": 23.185712432800003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこともあったわね\nデビューしたのは私の方が先だったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That happened too\nI debuted before her‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3857122421,
      "endTime": 29.671473407700002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あっという間に追い抜かれて\n麻奈ちゃんに差をつけられちゃったのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She quickly overtook me\nand I felt the difference between me and Mana-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8648065885,
      "endTime": 34.820565223699994,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6468.526744799999,
          "startTime": 36.3333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6289.091968499999,
          "startTime": 36.153898557
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.953898557
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.953898557
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_fan-07.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、大好きーーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ I love youーー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0205657323,
      "endTime": 39.6538988114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.9205657323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "観客A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Audience",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "見ろよ、あそこのステージ！　盛り上がり方が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ that stage! The excitement was",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9205657323,
      "endTime": 42.966666412399995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "観客A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Audience",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "尋常じゃないぞ！　やっぱ長瀬麻奈凄いな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "incredible! As expected‚ Mana Nagase is amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9666664124,
      "endTime": 47.9332856495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.0599513053
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.0599513053
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈ちゃんのステージ、物凄い人の数だわ）\n（一体何千人集まっているのかしら）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana-chan's stage‚ what a huge crowd）\n（How many thousands of people are there）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1599561373,
      "endTime": 57.9488901774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.162223339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "（同じライブイベントに私も出演してるのに）\n（麻奈ちゃんは中央のメインステージで、私は……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm performing at the same live event）\n（Mana-chan is on the main stage in the center‚ and I…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.162223339,
      "endTime": 67.3786126772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.4952841758
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.4952841758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなー！\n短い時間だけど、私の歌を楽しんでいってね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyoneー!\nIt's only a short time‚ but please enjoy my song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5452841758,
      "endTime": 75.52023382179999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.8802388031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "（会場の隅にある小さなステージで、数えるほどしか）\n（いないお客さんに必死にアピールして……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（On a small stage in the corner of the venue‚ desperately appealing）\n（to the few guests who could be counted…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8802388031,
      "endTime": 84.35640533750001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.5497386137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "観客A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Audience",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最近アイドル増えたな、あの子も可愛いんだけどなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are a lot more idols these days‚ that girl is cute‚ tooー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5497386137,
      "endTime": 89.8999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "観客A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Audience",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いまいちパッとしないよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But doesn't really catch my eye",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.8999987285,
      "endTime": 91.79999974569999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob2",
      "speakerName": "観客B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Audience",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルって言ってもピンキリだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even among idols‚ there are many variations",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0666735333,
      "endTime": 95.06667251600001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob2",
      "speakerName": "観客B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Audience",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "無名のアイドルには興味ないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not interested in unknown idols",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.066672516,
      "endTime": 98.0018644808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2018646715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなステージの前を素通りして、足を止めてさえ）\n（くれない……麻奈ちゃんとは大違いだわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Everyone passes by the stage‚ and doesn't even）\n（stop… It's a big difference from Mana-chan）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2018646715,
      "endTime": 106.93333918270001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "（なんで売れないんだろう。何が足りないんだろう）\n（私じゃ無理なのかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Why am unpopular? What am I lacking?）\n（Is it too much for me…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2396538255,
      "endTime": 115.4333376568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.7793978847
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "（けど、諦めない……ソロでも頑張ればきっと……）\n（負けない、負けたくない、絶対売れてやるんだから！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ don't give up… If I try hard‚ even as a solo‚ I'm surely…）\n（I won't lose‚ I don't want to lose‚ I'll definitely become popular!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7793978847,
      "endTime": 125.7658588246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 126.8658588246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃の私は売れようと必死だったわ\nでも、どれだけ頑張っても見向きもされなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that time‚ I was desperate to become popular\nBut‚ no matter how hard I tried‚ no one paid any attention to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.9325265086,
      "endTime": 136.6705987131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-shj002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子にとっては、同じ事務所に長瀬麻奈という\n大スターがいたことが不運だった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko was unlucky to have a big star\nnamed Mana Nagase in the same office",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.8639317985,
      "endTime": 143.82329697560002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-shj003.m4a",
      "text": "常に麻奈と比較され、いい仕事は麻奈にばかり回って\nくる、そんな境遇では……いや、それは言い訳だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Always being compared to Mana‚ good things only coming\nto Mana‚ and in that situation… No‚ that's just an excuse",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.0166303471,
      "endTime": 156.466675742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-shj004.m4a",
      "text": "遙子にアイドルとしてのポテンシャルがあったことは\n今の人気が証明している",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko's current popularity proves that\nshe has potential as an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.653342485,
      "endTime": 161.8576508041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-shj005.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃、仕事を取ってこられなかったのは……\n遙子の素質を活かすことが出来なかったのは俺の責任だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that time‚ I couldn't take her work…\nIt's my fault that I couldn't make the most of Haruko's talent",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.090975904,
      "endTime": 171.92473978950002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
