      "text": "遙子は昔からそうだったな。麻奈の人気を妬むどころか\nいつも麻奈を応援して、支えていた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko has always been like that. Far from being jealous of Mana's popularity‚\nshe always supported and encouraged her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.5639403499,
      "endTime": 190.2999956768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
