      "text": "羨む気持ちはありましたよ。でも、それ以上に\n麻奈ちゃんは星見プロの仲間で大事な友達ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did feel envious. But more than that‚\nMana-chan is a colleague at Hoshimi Prods. and a dear friend",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.64542613,
      "endTime": 200.0999855043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
