      "text": "……それに、麻奈ちゃんと約束したんです\nいつか必ず、二人でステージに立とうって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…And I promised Mana-chan\nSomeday‚ two of us would must stand on stage together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.6534977116,
      "endTime": 209.2666552228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
