      "text": "（事務所は期待の新人にかかりきりになって、結果を）\n（出せない役立たずはさらに立場を失うだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The office will be preoccupied with the promising new talent‚ and the useless talent）\n（that doesn't produce results will lose even more ground）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 373.8275798318,
      "endTime": 382.0333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk030.m4a",
      "text": "（それでも、新しい後輩に興味はあった。麻奈ちゃん）\n（という後輩に、私は何度も勇気づけられてきたから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Still‚ I was interested in the new junior talent. I have gained）\n（courage many times from my junior named Mana-chan）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 382.2876829304,
      "endTime": 391.9737436451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk031.m4a",
      "text": "（新しく入ってくる子は）\n（私にどんな影響を与えてくれるだろう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What kind of influence）\n（will the new girl have on me…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 392.3070749439,
      "endTime": 397.3303548651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数ヶ月後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few months later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 398.2436539805,
      "endTime": 399.27696086530005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 399.3436275319
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか、遙子さん？\n星見プロの期待の新人は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think‚ Haruko-san?\nHoshimi Prod's promising new talents",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 402.2436923817,
      "endTime": 406.7774565534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk032.m4a",
      "text": "みんな素直でやる気があって、何よりとても可愛いわ\n若いっていいわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They are all honest‚ motivated‚ and above all‚ really cute\nIt's good to be young…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 406.9641232963,
      "endTime": 414.3819788452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんだって十分若いですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're still young‚ Haruko-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 414.588645283,
      "endTime": 417.6077836669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk033.m4a",
      "text": "ありがと。でも、私はあの子達とは違うから\n自分の可能性を信じて未来を夢見る彼女達とは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. But I'm not like those girls\nThey believe in their own potential and dream of a brighter future…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 417.8144502954,
      "endTime": 428.4246071176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk034.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば聞いたわよ。オーディション合格組とは別で\nさくらちゃんを中心にしたユニットを作るそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I heard. It looks like they're going to create a unit\ncentered around Sakura-chan‚ separate from the audition winners",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 428.7712717689,
      "endTime": 436.4454463638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、太陽のように輝くアイドルグループをと\n考えています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm thinking of creating an idol group\nthat shines as brightly as the sun",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 436.6321131067,
      "endTime": 441.63311093600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、メンバーの選考が難航していて……\n遙子さんはどんな子がいいと思いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ they're having trouble selecting members…\nHaruko-san‚ what kind of girl do you think would be good?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 441.8197776314,
      "endTime": 449.4180173392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk035.m4a",
      "text": "私が選ぶなら？　そうね……\nやっぱり、アイドルへの想いが強い子かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I were to choose? Well…\nOf course‚ I'll choose a girl with a strong desire to become an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 449.6313505009,
      "endTime": 458.6197173908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk036.m4a",
      "text": "才能がなくても、向いていなくても、アイドルとして\n輝きたい……挑戦せずにはいられない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if she doesn't have talent‚ not cut out‚ wants to shine\nas an idol… can't help but try…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 458.8330508387,
      "endTime": 467.5332841075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk037.m4a",
      "text": "そんな夢と希望に満ちた子に、私は輝いてほしいわ\n私は夢も希望も、とっくに失っちゃったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want a girl like that‚ full of dreams and hope‚ to shine\nI lost my dreams and hopes a long time ago…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 467.7466174598,
      "endTime": 478.2980460639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんですか、頑張り続ける遙子さんが\n夢も希望も失っているはずないじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about‚ Haruko-san keeps working hard\nThere's no way you're lost your dreams and hopes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 478.4980458732,
      "endTime": 485.792717218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは今でも自分の可能性を信じている……\nそれは、そばで見ている俺がよく分かっています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san still believes in your own potential…\nI know that very well‚ having watched from the side",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 486.0793898738,
      "endTime": 494.590637318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk038.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なのかしら……\n私はまだ、輝けるのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that… so…\nAm I‚ still shining…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 494.7973041372,
      "endTime": 502.2333707173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk039.m4a",
      "text": "（こんな私でも、さくらちゃんと一緒なら……）\n（眩しく輝く太陽のようなメンバーと一緒なら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even someone like me‚ if I'm with Sakura-chan…）\n（With members who shine like dazzling sunshine…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 502.5740823583,
      "endTime": 511.9154880362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_04-hrk040.m4a",
      "text": "（きっとこれは、アイドルとして輝く最後のチャンス）\n（私を新ユニットのメンバーに選んでもらえたら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is surely my last chance to shine as an idol）\n（If they choose me to be a member of their new unit…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 512.4088091053,
      "endTime": 520.8770181812,
